            "answer_text": "How to write an application for leaving early. This is a sample (draft) format of an application for your reference. (Date) To, The HR Manager (company name) (Place) Subject: Application seeking permission to leave early. Respected Sir/Ma'am, I would like to leave early from the office tomorrow i.e. xx-xx-xxxx (date) as I have an appointment with the dentist for my daughter at 4 pm. Therefore, I request you to please grant me a permission to leave the Office after 3 p.m. tomorrow so that I can take her to the hospital. Please contact me on my personal phone if you have any doubts or queries about the current project. Thanking in anticipation. Sincerely, (Your name) (ID No.) (Your job position) (Company name)  I hope this answer is helpful to you. Thank you. ",
